        </caption>
        <graphic xlink:href="1471-2105-12-199-3"/>
      </fig>
      <p>The processed results displayed on the Web page include the candidate epitope and the alignments for all mimotope sequences with their <italic>P</italic>-value scores. These results can be viewed in either text/table or 3D graphics through Jmol [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="B35">35</xref>] that can be adjusted by changing some parameters (Figure <xref ref-type="fig" rid="F4">4</xref>).</p>
